query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS auto_targeting_settings (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  campaign_id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  ad_group_id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  targeting_type ENUM('close_match', 'loose_match', 'substitutes', 'complements') NOT NULL,
  targeting_status ENUM('enabled', 'paused') DEFAULT 'enabled',
  bid DECIMAL(10, 2),
  suggested_bid DECIMAL(10, 2),
  bid_range_low DECIMAL(10, 2),
  bid_range_high DECIMAL(10, 2),
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  UNIQUE KEY unique_targeting (campaign_id, ad_group_id, targeting_type)
);
